showdown.abilities.prankster.name=Prankster
showdown.abilities.prankster.desc=This Pokémon's non-damaging moves have their priority increased by 1. Opposing Dark-type Pokémon are immune to these moves, and any move called by these moves, if the resulting user of the move has this Ability.
