showdown.abilities.pressure.name=Pressure
showdown.abilities.pressure.desc=If this Pokémon is the target of an opposing Pokémon's move, that move loses one additional PP. Imprison, Snatch, and Tera Blast also lose one additional PP when used by an opposing Pokémon, but Sticky Web does not.
