showdown.moves.fissure.name=Fissure
showdown.moves.fissure.desc=Deals damage to the target equal to the target's maximum HP. Ignores accuracy and evasiveness modifiers. This attack's accuracy is equal to (user's level - target's level + 30)%, and fails if the target is at a higher level. Pokémon with the Sturdy Ability are immune.
